Vinagre 0.4.90 (0.5 beta 1)
===========================

  Features

	+ Documentation (Jaap A. Haitsma and Vinicius Depizzol)
	+ Man page (Emilio Pozuelo Monfort)
	+ Make use of new gio instead of gnome-vfs
	+ Depends on gtk-vnc 0.3.2

  Fixes
	+ Minor fixes

